48
00:01:55,222 --> 00:01:55,722
<break time="0.5s"/>

49
00:01:55,722 --> 00:02:05,521
Yes. It's 077, 009, 382, 16. Once again,
077, 009, 382, 16.

50
00:02:05,521 --> 00:02:07,021
<break time="1.5s"/>

51
00:02:07,021 --> 00:02:09,854
