53
00:02:16,448 --> 00:02:17,948
<break time="1.5s"/>

54
00:02:17,948 --> 00:02:24,496
Okay, got it 16 Camden Grove, SE15, 3XB.

55
00:02:24,496 --> 00:02:28,088
I’m going to give you an incident
reference number, do you have something

56
00:02:28,088 --> 00:02:29,186
