58
00:02:30,186 --> 00:02:31,161
Yes, go ahead.

59
00:02:31,161 --> 00:02:34,923
Your incident reference number is 46195.

60
00:02:34,923 --> 00:02:35,223
<break time="0.3s"/>

61
00:02:35,223 --> 00:02:40,610
Please stay inside, keep yourself safe,
